snippet.title: Math Blaster Ages 7-8 Full Playthrough
snippet.description:
Math Blaster Ages 7-8 Full Playthrough

Math Blaster Ages 7-8 is a game created by Knowledge Adventure and Davidson and Associates Inc. in 2000. It was also known as Math Blaster for 2nd grade. The game features Max Blaster, Galactic Commander (GC), and their robotic dog, MEL.
